  "abstract": "The goal of the International Crops Research Institute for\r\nthe Semi-Arid Tropics (ICRISAT) is to harness the power\r\nof technology for development, food security, poverty\r\nalleviation and environmental protection, targeted at\r\npoor rural families in the semi-arid tropics (SAT) of the\r\nworld. But ICRISAT cannot do this alone. Countries, such\r\nas Sweden, help ICRISAT achieve this goal through their\r\nsupport and encouragement, as well as through financial\r\nassistance...",
